0.3.name: wordpress/lastfm-recent-tracks-widget
0.3.description: The Last.fm Recent Tracks Plugin / Widget let's you display your Last.fm recent tracks in the sidebar of your blog, useful if you use WP-Cache / Super Cache and want the feed to be fresh. It leverages jQuery and JSONP to provide a never-stale, asynchronous connection to Last.fm.
